Neiman Marcus Dip
  --Cook's Country

8 slices bacon, cut into 1/2" pieces
8 oz extra-sharp cheddar cheese, shredded (2 c)
1 c mayo
1/2 c slivered almonds, toasted
4 scallions, sliced thin
2 tsp hot sauce

Cook bacon in 12" nonstick skillet over medium heat until crispy, 5-7 min. Using slotted spoon, transfer bacon to paper towel–lined plate; let cool for 5 min. Stir cheddar, mayonnaise, almonds, scallions, hot sauce, and bacon in bowl until thoroughly combined. Cover and refrigerate for at least 2 hr or up to 2 days. Serve.


Notes: recommined Frank’s RedHot Original Cayenne Pepper Sauce 
